# Orphaned Images Bug

## Status: DOCUMENTED

This document tracks a known issue with orphaned images.

## Issue

When slides are deleted from stories, their associated media files may remain in storage.

## Impact

- Storage bloat over time
- No functional impact on users

## Proposed Solution

1. Track slide deletions
2. Implement cleanup job
3. Add storage usage monitoring

## Workaround

Manual cleanup via Supabase Storage dashboard.
